com.rakuten.android.ads.runa

Enum ErrorState


  • public enum ErrorState

    Indicates the status when an error occurred in AdRequest.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • UNFILLED

        public static ErrorState UNFILLED

        The ad request was successful, but no ad was returned due to lack of ad inventory.

      • FATAL_ERROR

        public static ErrorState FATAL_ERROR

        The ad request was invalid. For instance, the ad spot ID was incorrect.

      • NETWORK_ERROR

        public static ErrorState NETWORK_ERROR

        The ad request was unsuccessful due to network connectivity.

      • INTERNAL_ERROR

        public static ErrorState INTERNAL_ERROR

        Something happened internally. For instance, an invalid response was received from the ad server.
